  "instructions": [
    "Roast the coconut milk in a skillet until slightly thickened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Dice the ginger and mince garlic cloves. Set aside.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together lemon juice, tahini sauce, salt, and dill seeds with cumin seeds. Slowly add to the roasted coconut milk while stirring continuously.",
    "Blend in minced ginger and garlic until smooth.",
    "Fold in fresh cilantro leaves. Taste and adjust seasonings if needed.",
    "Serve hot over steamed basmati rice or as a side dish."
